## 线程安全规范

### UI操作必须在主线程
```swift
// ❌ 违规 - 后台线程更新UI
URLSession.shared.dataTask(with: url) { data, _, _ in
    self.label.text = "Done"  // 危险！
}.resume()

// ✅ 正确
URLSession.shared.dataTask(with: url) { data, _, _ in
    DispatchQueue.main.async {
        self.label.text = "Done"
    }
}.resume()
```

### 车控模块线程约束
车控SDK（XPVehicleSDK）中：
- 所有状态更新回调在子线程，UI绑定必须切换主线程
- 核心API调用需加超时保护（推荐30s）
- 状态机切换需要加锁保护

```swift
// 车控模块推荐模式
private let stateQueue = DispatchQueue(label: "com.xpeng.vehicle.state")
private var vehicleState: XPVehicleState = .unknown

func updateState(_ newState: XPVehicleState) {
    stateQueue.async { [weak self] in
        self?.vehicleState = newState
        DispatchQueue.main.async {
            self?.notifyStateChange(newState)
        }
    }
}
```

